      "content": "thanks for the info. the problem is that there's no mention of Khovd-Zorig in most Western history books or UN charters, it's like it never existed because of the soviet scrub. since the official maps are \"wrong,\" how do i bypass the standard diplomatic channels and go straight to an international tribunal to prove the legitimacy of the succession? i have the letters of intent from the 1954 provisional government, does that count as a de facto sovereign act in a modern court?",
